'Quad play is proving all the rage amongst telecoms providers, but mobile often seems like the afterthought of these four-way bundles.

'Many customers are already tied into long contracts so aren't in the market for a new mobile deal.

'The advantage is that all your services are under one roof, making billing far simpler, but if one service isn't up to scratch, it can be harder to leave.  

